<Content>Convenient hotel for further travelling by bus After a long flight from Europe, this hotel is convenient as it is not far from the airport (by taxi). And as we planned to travel by bus to Quer茅taro by bus, Brasilia is a good choice because it is only 7 minutes by foot from Terminale Norte. However, I wouldn't stay here to visit Mexico City but advise to rather stay in a hotel in the historical center as the environment of this hotel is not so spectacular. Besides, rooms can be noisy and I would recommand to ask for a room that not faces the street. We paid 380 mexican pesos for a double room. 
