<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Super value great location. This hotel is located just a few steps from the northern bus station (Terminal del Norte) and the metro is there as well, putting all attractions in easy reach. Buses for Teotihuacan leave from Terminal Norte. Hotel is clean and comfortable, in another location this hotel would cost $100.00 per night. As it is the rate for a single is only about $18.00. There is a full service restaurant, and a Bar which often has live music. 
